singam ii is a 2013 indian tamil action masala film written and directed by hari . the film features suriya and anushka shetty in the lead roles . the film was produced by s. lakshman kumar under the banner of &lt;unk&gt; films . the film is produced by s. lakshman kumar kumar and produced by s. ganesh kumar . the film was released worldwide on 5 february 2013 .